				<span>Amuse-bouche</span>
			</dt>
			<dd>
				<div>
					Deals water damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and applies one of the following effects based<br>on the user's current cooking stance:<br><br>Appetizer Stance: Inflicts frostbite and<br>reduces enemies' defense by 5% for 30 seconds.<br>This defense reduction effect will not stack.<br><br>Entrée Stance: Inflicts stun and<br>reduces enemies' strength by 15% for 30 seconds.<br>This strength reduction effect will not stack.<br><br>Dessert Stance: Inflicts freeze.
				</div>
			</dd>
	<dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/944f49691bf38a5e905697ff03d017ad2.png"></span>
